    Don't use dangerous machinery while or soon after listening to the output of
this program. Wait until you are alert.

    The following people should not use this program:
    -people using pacemakers.
    -people prone to seizures or epilepsy.
    -people suffering from heart disorders.
    -people taking psychoactive drugs, stimulents or tranquillizers.
    -people undergoing psychiatric treatment.

Sorry about all the warnings, but it had to be done.

    The settings saved in the presets drawer are only experimental values
suggested by various documents on the www. Take them with a pinch of salt! Some
of the effects may not exist, such as earth-resonance, which is supposed to make
the user feel in tune with the planet, or OOBE which are supposed to help the
user have an out of body experience, or healing-of-the-body.
