@node "Sys" "System requirements"

  To run this, you need:

  An Amiga. I havn't tested it on UAE but I doubt it'll work.
  About 0.9 Mb free ram, of which about 0.6 Mb has to be chip ram.
  Gadtools (contained in version 2.x and 3.x systems).
@endnode

