@node "Intro" "Introduction"

  This program generates binaural beats and pink noise, which together should
allow you to enter various states of consciousness which are not attainable
without a lot of practice otherwise. These can be used for meditation,
relaxation, sleep induction, sleep replacement, and various other things.

  The Monroe Institute offers courses and hardware which should be more
effective than this program, but use similar methods for the aural stimulus.
There are various other boxes available, and a fair few tapes, and a program
(for 'doze 95), if you want an alternative.

  The idea is that you relax lying down with your eyes closed, and listen to the
output of this program for half an hour or so, and your brainwaves should follow
the frequency of the binaural beat in a frequency following response (ffr). This
alters the state of your consciousness. For more information, click @{"here" link binbeainfo}.

@endnode

